# Sport Photography Gallery

This directory should contain your sport photography collection.

## Required Images:
Add 6 or more images named:
- sport-1.jpg
- sport-2.jpg
- sport-3.jpg
- sport-4.jpg
- sport-5.jpg
- sport-6.jpg
- (continue numbering as needed)

## Specifications:
- Dimensions: 1200x1600px or higher (3:4 aspect ratio / portrait)
- Format: JPG (optimized for web, under 300KB each recommended)
- Content: Your best sport photography - action shots, athletes, competitions, training moments

## How to Add:
1. Select your best sport photographs
2. Rename them following the numbering pattern (sport-1.jpg, sport-2.jpg, etc.)
3. Place them in `/public/photos/sport/`
4. If adding more than 6, also update `/app/portfolio/[category]/page.tsx` to include additional photo entries

The gallery will display these in a responsive 3-column grid on desktop, 2 columns on tablet, and 1 column on mobile.
